{
  "video_id": "UG_X_7g63rY",
  "title": "How I'm fighting bias in algorithms | Joy Buolamwini",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12861.0,
      "end_time": 15995.0,
      "text": "Hello, I&#39;m Joy, a poet of code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16180.0,
      "end_time": 21120.0,
      "text": "on a mission to stop an unseen force that&#39;s rising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21360.0,
      "end_time": 23892.0,
      "text": "a force that I called \"the coded gaze,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23916.0,
      "end_time": 27225.0,
      "text": "my term for algorithmic bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27249.0,
      "end_time": 31549.0,
      "text": "Algorithmic bias, like human bias, results in unfairness."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31573.0,
      "end_time": 37595.0,
      "text": "However, algorithms, like viruses, can spread bias on a massive scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 37619.0,
      "end_time": 39201.0,
      "text": "at a rapid pace."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39763.0,
      "end_time": 44150.0,
      "text": "Algorithmic bias can also lead to exclusionary experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44174.0,
      "end_time": 46302.0,
      "text": "and discriminatory practices."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46326.0,
      "end_time": 48387.0,
      "text": "Let me show you what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 51236.0,
      "text": "(Video) Joy Buolamwini: Hi, camera. I&#39;ve got a face."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51982.0,
      "end_time": 53846.0,
      "text": "Can you see my face?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53871.0,
      "end_time": 55496.0,
      "text": "No-glasses face?"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55521.0,
      "end_time": 57735.0,
      "text": "You can see her face."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58570.0,
      "end_time": 60302.0,
      "text": "What about my face?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63710.0,
      "end_time": 67460.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve got a mask. Can you see my mask?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 68294.0,
      "end_time": 70658.0,
      "text": "Joy Buolamwini: So how did this happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70683.0,
      "end_time": 73824.0,
      "text": "Why am I sitting in front of a computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73848.0,
      "end_time": 75272.0,
      "text": "in a white mask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75296.0,
      "end_time": 78946.0,
      "text": "trying to be detected by a cheap webcam?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 78970.0,
      "end_time": 81261.0,
      "text": "Well, when I&#39;m not fighting the coded gaze"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81285.0,
      "end_time": 82804.0,
      "text": "as a poet of code,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82829.0,
      "end_time": 86101.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a graduate student at the MIT Media Lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86125.0,
      "end_time": 91420.0,
      "text": "and there I have the opportunity to work on all sorts of whimsical projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91660.0,
      "end_time": 93930.0,
      "text": "including the Aspire Mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93117.0,
      "end_time": 98251.0,
      "text": "a project I did so I could project digital masks onto my reflection."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 98275.0,
      "end_time": 100625.0,
      "text": "So in the morning, if I wanted to feel powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100649.0,
      "end_time": 102830.0,
      "text": "I could put on a lion."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 102107.0,
      "end_time": 105603.0,
      "text": "If I wanted to be uplifted, I might have a quote."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 105627.0,
      "end_time": 108616.0,
      "text": "So I used generic facial recognition software"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108640.0,
      "end_time": 109991.0,
      "text": "to build the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110150.0,
      "end_time": 115118.0,
      "text": "but found it was really hard to test it unless I wore a white mask."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116102.0,
      "end_time": 120448.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I&#39;ve run into this issue before."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120472.0,
      "end_time": 124774.0,
      "text": "When I was an undergraduate at Georgia Tech studying computer science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 124799.0,
      "end_time": 126854.0,
      "text": "I used to work on social robots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126878.0,
      "end_time": 130655.0,
      "text": "and one of my tasks was to get a robot to play peek-a-boo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130679.0,
      "end_time": 132362.0,
      "text": "a simple turn-taking game"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132386.0,
      "end_time": 136707.0,
      "text": "where partners cover their face and then uncover it saying, \"Peek-a-boo!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 136731.0,
      "end_time": 141160.0,
      "text": "The problem is, peek-a-boo doesn&#39;t really work if I can&#39;t see you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 141184.0,
      "end_time": 143683.0,
      "text": "and my robot couldn&#39;t see me."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143707.0,
      "end_time": 147656.0,
      "text": "But I borrowed my roommate&#39;s face to get the project done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147681.0,
      "end_time": 149610.0,
      "text": "submitted the assignment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149850.0,
      "end_time": 152838.0,
      "text": "and figured, you know what, somebody else will solve this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 153489.0,
      "end_time": 155492.0,
      "text": "Not too long after,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155516.0,
      "end_time": 159674.0,
      "text": "I was in Hong Kong for an entrepreneurship competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160159.0,
      "end_time": 162852.0,
      "text": "The organizers decided to take participants"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 162877.0,
      "end_time": 165249.0,
      "text": "on a tour of local start-ups."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165273.0,
      "end_time": 167988.0,
      "text": "One of the start-ups had a social robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168120.0,
      "end_time": 169924.0,
      "text": "and they decided to do a demo."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169948.0,
      "end_time": 172928.0,
      "text": "The demo worked on everybody until it got to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172952.0,
      "end_time": 174875.0,
      "text": "and you can probably guess it."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 174899.0,
      "end_time": 177864.0,
      "text": "It couldn&#39;t detect my face."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 177888.0,
      "end_time": 180399.0,
      "text": "I asked the developers what was going on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 180423.0,
      "end_time": 185956.0,
      "text": "and it turned out we had used the same generic facial recognition software."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 185980.0,
      "end_time": 187630.0,
      "text": "Halfway around the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187654.0,
      "end_time": 191506.0,
      "text": "I learned that algorithmic bias can travel as quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191530.0,
      "end_time": 194700.0,
      "text": "as it takes to download some files off of the internet."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 195565.0,
      "end_time": 198641.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s going on? Why isn&#39;t my face being detected?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198665.0,
      "end_time": 202210.0,
      "text": "Well, we have to look at how we give machines sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 202450.0,
      "end_time": 205453.0,
      "text": "Computer vision uses machine learning techniques"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205478.0,
      "end_time": 207358.0,
      "text": "to do facial recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207382.0,
      "end_time": 211279.0,
      "text": "So how this works is, you create a training set with examples of faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211303.0,
      "end_time": 214121.0,
      "text": "This is a face. This is a face. This is not a face."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 214145.0,
      "end_time": 218664.0,
      "text": "And over time, you can teach a computer how to recognize other faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 218688.0,
      "end_time": 222677.0,
      "text": "However, if the training sets aren&#39;t really that diverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 222701.0,
      "end_time": 226490.0,
      "text": "any face that deviates too much from the established norm"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226740.0,
      "end_time": 227723.0,
      "text": "will be harder to detect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227747.0,
      "end_time": 229710.0,
      "text": "which is what was happening to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 229734.0,
      "end_time": 232116.0,
      "text": "But don&#39;t worry -- there&#39;s some good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 232140.0,
      "end_time": 234910.0,
      "text": "Training sets don&#39;t just materialize out of nowhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 234935.0,
      "end_time": 236723.0,
      "text": "We actually can create them."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 236747.0,
      "end_time": 240923.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s an opportunity to create full-spectrum training sets"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240947.0,
      "end_time": 244771.0,
      "text": "that reflect a richer portrait of humanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 244795.0,
      "end_time": 247160.0,
      "text": "Now you&#39;ve seen in my examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247400.0,
      "end_time": 248808.0,
      "text": "how social robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248832.0,
      "end_time": 253442.0,
      "text": "was how I found out about exclusion with algorithmic bias."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253467.0,
      "end_time": 258282.0,
      "text": "But algorithmic bias can also lead to discriminatory practices."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 259257.0,
      "end_time": 260709.0,
      "text": "Across the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 260733.0,
      "end_time": 264931.0,
      "text": "police departments are starting to use facial recognition software"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264956.0,
      "end_time": 267415.0,
      "text": "in their crime-fighting arsenal."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 267439.0,
      "end_time": 269452.0,
      "text": "Georgetown Law published a report"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269476.0,
      "end_time": 276239.0,
      "text": "showing that one in two adults in the US -- that&#39;s 117 million people --"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 276263.0,
      "end_time": 279796.0,
      "text": "have their faces in facial recognition networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 279821.0,
      "end_time": 284373.0,
      "text": "Police departments can currently look at these networks unregulated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 284397.0,
      "end_time": 288683.0,
      "text": "using algorithms that have not been audited for accuracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 288707.0,
      "end_time": 292570.0,
      "text": "Yet we know facial recognition is not fail proof,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292595.0,
      "end_time": 296774.0,
      "text": "and labeling faces consistently remains a challenge."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296798.0,
      "end_time": 298560.0,
      "text": "You might have seen this on Facebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298584.0,
      "end_time": 301572.0,
      "text": "My friends and I laugh all the time when we see other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 301596.0,
      "end_time": 304540.0,
      "text": "mislabeled in our photos."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 304780.0,
      "end_time": 309669.0,
      "text": "But misidentifying a suspected criminal is no laughing matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309693.0,
      "end_time": 312520.0,
      "text": "nor is breaching civil liberties."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 312544.0,
      "end_time": 315748.0,
      "text": "Machine learning is being used for facial recognition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 315773.0,
      "end_time": 320278.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also extending beyond the realm of computer vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 321860.0,
      "end_time": 325102.0,
      "text": "In her book, \"Weapons of Math Destruction,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 325126.0,
      "end_time": 331806.0,
      "text": "data scientist Cathy O&#39;Neil talks about the rising new WMDs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 331831.0,
      "end_time": 336184.0,
      "text": "widespread, mysterious and destructive algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336208.0,
      "end_time": 339172.0,
      "text": "that are increasingly being used to make decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 339196.0,
      "end_time": 342373.0,
      "text": "that impact more aspects of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342397.0,
      "end_time": 344267.0,
      "text": "So who gets hired or fired?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 344291.0,
      "end_time": 346403.0,
      "text": "Do you get that loan? Do you get insurance?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 346427.0,
      "end_time": 349930.0,
      "text": "Are you admitted into the college you wanted to get into?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 349954.0,
      "end_time": 353463.0,
      "text": "Do you and I pay the same price for the same product"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 353487.0,
      "end_time": 355929.0,
      "text": "purchased on the same platform?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 355953.0,
      "end_time": 359712.0,
      "text": "Law enforcement is also starting to use machine learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 359736.0,
      "end_time": 362250.0,
      "text": "for predictive policing."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 362490.0,
      "end_time": 365543.0,
      "text": "Some judges use machine-generated risk scores to determine"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365567.0,
      "end_time": 369969.0,
      "text": "how long an individual is going to spend in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 369993.0,
      "end_time": 372447.0,
      "text": "So we really have to think about these decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 372471.0,
      "end_time": 373653.0,
      "text": "Are they fair?"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 373677.0,
      "end_time": 376567.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve seen that algorithmic bias"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376591.0,
      "end_time": 379965.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t necessarily always lead to fair outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 379989.0,
      "end_time": 381953.0,
      "text": "So what can we do about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 381977.0,
      "end_time": 385657.0,
      "text": "Well, we can start thinking about how we create more inclusive code"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 385681.0,
      "end_time": 388671.0,
      "text": "and employ inclusive coding practices."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 388695.0,
      "end_time": 391400.0,
      "text": "It really starts with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 391528.0,
      "end_time": 393489.0,
      "text": "So who codes matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 393513.0,
      "end_time": 397631.0,
      "text": "Are we creating full-spectrum teams with diverse individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 397656.0,
      "end_time": 400670.0,
      "text": "who can check each other&#39;s blind spots?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 400910.0,
      "end_time": 403636.0,
      "text": "On the technical side, how we code matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 403660.0,
      "end_time": 407311.0,
      "text": "Are we factoring in fairness as we&#39;re developing systems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 407335.0,
      "end_time": 410248.0,
      "text": "And finally, why we code matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410605.0,
      "end_time": 415688.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve used tools of computational creation to unlock immense wealth."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 415712.0,
      "end_time": 420159.0,
      "text": "We now have the opportunity to unlock even greater equality"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 420183.0,
      "end_time": 423113.0,
      "text": "if we make social change a priority"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 423137.0,
      "end_time": 425307.0,
      "text": "and not an afterthought."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 425828.0,
      "end_time": 430349.0,
      "text": "And so these are the three tenets that will make up the \"incoding\" movement."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 430374.0,
      "end_time": 432260.0,
      "text": "Who codes matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 432500.0,
      "end_time": 433593.0,
      "text": "how we code matters"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 433617.0,
      "end_time": 435640.0,
      "text": "and why we code matters."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 435664.0,
      "end_time": 438763.0,
      "text": "So to go towards incoding, we can start thinking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 438787.0,
      "end_time": 441950.0,
      "text": "building platforms that can identify bias"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 441975.0,
      "end_time": 445530.0,
      "text": "by collecting people&#39;s experiences like the ones I shared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 445770.0,
      "end_time": 448147.0,
      "text": "but also auditing existing software."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 448171.0,
      "end_time": 451936.0,
      "text": "We can also start to create more inclusive training sets."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 451960.0,
      "end_time": 454763.0,
      "text": "Imagine a \"Selfies for Inclusion\" campaign"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 454787.0,
      "end_time": 458441.0,
      "text": "where you and I can help developers test and create"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 458466.0,
      "end_time": 460559.0,
      "text": "more inclusive training sets."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 461122.0,
      "end_time": 463950.0,
      "text": "And we can also start thinking more conscientiously"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 463974.0,
      "end_time": 469365.0,
      "text": "about the social impact of the technology that we&#39;re developing."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 469389.0,
      "end_time": 471782.0,
      "text": "To get the incoding movement started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 471806.0,
      "end_time": 474652.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve launched the Algorithmic Justice League,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 474677.0,
      "end_time": 480549.0,
      "text": "where anyone who cares about fairness can help fight the coded gaze."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 480573.0,
      "end_time": 483869.0,
      "text": "On codedgaze.com, you can report bias,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 483893.0,
      "end_time": 486337.0,
      "text": "request audits, become a tester"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 486362.0,
      "end_time": 489133.0,
      "text": "and join the ongoing conversation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 489157.0,
      "end_time": 491443.0,
      "text": "#codedgaze."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 492562.0,
      "end_time": 495490.0,
      "text": "So I invite you to join me"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 495730.0,
      "end_time": 498792.0,
      "text": "in creating a world where technology works for all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 498816.0,
      "end_time": 500712.0,
      "text": "not just some of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 500737.0,
      "end_time": 505325.0,
      "text": "a world where we value inclusion and center social change."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 505349.0,
      "end_time": 506524.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 506548.0,
      "end_time": 510819.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 512693.0,
      "end_time": 515547.0,
      "text": "But I have one question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 515571.0,
      "end_time": 517630.0,
      "text": "Will you join me in the fight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
